@node Menus "TRC User's Guide | Reference | Menus"
@toc  Contents
@{u}@{b}Menus@{ub}@{uu}

@{b}Project@{ub}

   New         Presents a fresh game - a map with all counters off board.

   Open...     Presents a file requester allowing the player to load a
               previously saved game.

   Save        Saves the game.
   
   Save As...  Presents a file requester allowing the user to select or
               provide a file name to save the game to.

   About...    Displays program version and copyright information.

   Quit        Quits.


@{b}View@{ub}

   Russian Counter Mix     Opens the Russian Counter Mix window, or brings
                           it to the front and makes it active if already
                           open.

   German Counter Mix      Opens the German Counter Mix window, or brings
                           it to the front and makes it active if already
                           open.

   Combat Results Table    Opens the CRT window, or brings it to the front
                           and makes it active if already open.

@endnode
